room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Houdini's Room Escape in Cincinnati
review: Exceptional place! We had game master Hannah for the lab and game master Sarah for the Speak Easy. Both extraordinary m, friendly, and welcoming. Love that this business is handicap friendly. AMAZING EXPERIENCE. Next time in Cincinnati, will do the Oval Office and game room!

room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Houdini's Room Escape in Cincinnati
review: Our family had such a fun time at Houdini's doing the Speakeasy. Easily one of the best escape room experiences Ive had. Shout out to Zac for being a great host. We definitely plan to come back for more rooms.

room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Houdini's Room Escape in Cincinnati
review: The Speakeasy was fun and challenging! Very conceptual in thought process and the clues were thought provoking.....escaped with :16 seconds remaining!
